$ Office Ribbon: File -> Options -> Trust Center -> Settings -> Macro Settings
@ Protected View

*Protected View* opens potentially harmful files (such as those that originate from an «unsafe location») in a *restricted mode* which minimizes the security problems such files might cause).

sa:
  The → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/ProtectedViewWindow[`ProtectedViewWindow` object] of the → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model.
